    httr (>= 1.3),
    R6 (>= 2.3),
    raster (>= 2.6),
    tools (>= 3.5),
    XML (>= 3.86),
    askpass (>= 1.1)
License: GPL (>= 3.0)
URL: https://github.com/norival/theiaR
BugReports: https://github.com/norival/theiaR/issues
Encoding: UTF-8
